<p><strong>Best time to go: </strong>May-June &amp; September-October are cooler for walking, but if you love the heat, head out in high summer and spend your days sipping an Aperol spritz by the lakeside, or head up into to the mountains for some cooler walks</p>
<p><strong>Best for: </strong>All walking abilities, sightseeing, activities</p>
<p><strong>Arrive into: </strong>Milan Malpensa (approx. 2 hours) or Como St Giovanni train station (approx. 14 hours from London St. Pancras)</p>
