<p><strong>Transfer Time:</strong> approx. 1 hour 30 mins from Milan Airport or approx. 1 hour from Como St Giovanni train station</p>
<p><strong>24/7 Support and advice:</strong> In person or over the phone from our local resort team based in Lake Como</p>]]></insidersGuide>
